## Golf Angular
## Development server
npm install
ng serve

## Build
ng build

## Node version 
8.9.4

## Node 8.11.1 version install
curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_8.x | sudo -E bash -
sudo apt-get install -y nodejs

## nvm install
curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/creationix/nvm/v0.33.11/install.sh | bash

## node 8.9.4 install
nvm install 8.9.4
nvm use 8.9.4

## installation problem (node-sass is not working on node 8.11.1)
cd node_modules/node-sass
npm install
node scripts/build -f

## Copy dist directory to delopy directoy
cp dist /var/www/html
